an_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Akuila Rokolisoa opened the scoring in the first minute with a try which he converted himself and he would add another try to his tally in the second half.\", \"from\": 303, \"to\": 458, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fehi Fineanganofo scored back to back tries in the first half, while Ngarohi McGarvey-Black also dotted down for two five pointers.\", \"from\": 460, \"to\": 591, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 529, \"end\": 551, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ngarohi_McGarvey-Black\", \"score\": 0.9999999999131433, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ngarohi McGarvey-Black\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ngarohi_McGarvey-Black\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ngarohi_McGarvey-Black\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Moses Leo scores for New Zealand All Blacks Sevens v South Africa.Photo:Iain McGregor / www.photosport.nz  They had a much tougher battle against South Africa, taking the match 17-5.\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 599, \"end\": 602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Phokas_the_Younger\", \"score\": 0.9635499756612017, \"rank\": 0.03782540696377702, \"text\": \"Leo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Phokas_the_Younger\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Phokas_the_Younger\"}, {\"begin\": 614, \"end\": 636, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.795924004091597e-16, \"text\": \"New Zealand All Blacks\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 739, \"end\": 751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9906627715175644, \"rank\": 0.00942259304699827, \"text\": \"South Af